OL,3,CIncome tax to rise from 20% to 22% in
OL,4,Cthe Isle of Man
OL,6,FTreasury Minister, Dr Alex Allinson,
OL,7,Fdescribed this year's plan for Manx
OL,8,Ffinances as a 'difficult budget', and
OL,9,Fone that was formed 'in very difficult
OL,10,Fcircumstances'.
OL,12,FWithin his speech in Tynwald, Dr
OL,13,FAllinson said: "The changes that I
OL,14,Fannounce today should be seen as the
OL,15,Fstart of a process of moving toward a
OL,16,Fdifferent approach to taxation.
