OL,6,FWhen asked about the threat of
OL,7,Frecession in the UK, Dr Allinson said:
OL,8,F"I think the Isle of Man is in a
OL,9,Fslightly different situation to the
OL,10,FUnited Kingdom.
OL,12,F"But we do know that the local economy
OL,13,Fhas been affected by higher prices".
OL,15,FDespite continued departmental
OL,16,Foverspend, all government departments
OL,17,Fare expected to receive additional
OL,18,Ffunds.
